<div class="jumbotron bg-green">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-sm-9 col-xs-12">
      <h2>Welcome, fellow students!</h2>
      <p>This application was made to help you track your grades in your college curriculum and properly weigh grades based on your course criteria.</p>
      <p>
        {{#if session.isAuthenticated}}
          {{#link-to 'dashboard.index' class='btn btn-outline btn-flat'}}
            Go to Dashboard
          {{/link-to}}
        {{else}}
          <a class="btn btn-flat btn-outline" href="#" role="button">Learn more</a>
        {{/if}}
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 hidden-xs">
      <h1 class='container-icon'>{{fa-icon 'file-text-o' size=2}}</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <h3>Courses</h3>
        <p>Keep track of your entire college curriculum by semester and cumulatively by adding multiple courses to your highly customizable profile. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <h3>Grades</h3>
        <p>Fill out your assignments, homeworks, and exams to the best of your ability and it will accurately represent these into your current grade. </p>
     </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <h3>Weights</h3>
        <p>All courses can be weighted to do all the heavy lifting for you to calculate your grades without having to even touch a calculator.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
